%8B%E5%8F%AF%E7%96%91%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E6%B6%89%E5%8F%8A%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1-%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%87%E8%BB%92%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:06:52.000Z","msg":"港共無所不用其技<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3d7be0e31c7d12d622820187894ee80a2e77ff","tid":2488381,"uid":87985,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:14:36.000Z","msg":"佢之前生日，星火有幫佢出post 徵寫信師<br />\n都有相關話題建議<br />\n大家有興趣可以寫信畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmemKFNCRG9J2ZmM5uHHKvidEuSqEZoViyvgj6eKcdpTAZ?filename=mjTZoF2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjTZoF2.png&h=c8486a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCredit:星火fb"},{"pid":"37ac4480e326750fa7c0fbaa0ea172c860a6e8cf","tid":2488381,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:16:24.000Z","msg":"睇嚟共產黨一定要入肥佬黎同搞一單&quot;外國勢力&quot;證據!"},{"pid":"35999ceb7fddcfd91edad9131416294ce2a0eaa0","tid":2488381,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db880080da81e404759ae140d445f4bfd3c7dad2","tid":2488381,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:17:32.000Z","msg":"屈到盡"},{"pid":"e85a472e8b37d4a9ffbf5ace9e30c035d1fd4280","tid":2488381,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:25:14.000Z","msg":"29歲律師助理涉嫌串謀黎智英協助李宇軒越邊境到台灣，另指他串謀黎、黎的前私人助理Mark Simon及現已流亡海外的「攬炒巴」劉祖迪請求外國制裁中國及香港，違反國安法。助理被控串謀勾結外國勢力等兩罪，案件今午於西九龍裁判法院再訊。控方指已索取被告及其他串謀人士的銀行戶口交易紀錄，尚待警方針對其中78項有可疑的紀錄作進一步調查。國安法指定法官、總裁判官蘇惠德押後案件至6月7日再訊，被告沒保釋申請，其間須繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方指控被告曾串謀他人，利用Stand With Hong Kong團隊（簡稱SWHK，即前「攬炒團隊」）以呼籲外國制裁中國及香港，並指控劉祖廸、李宇軒、Mark Simon及黎智英均為攬炒團隊的核心成員，其中劉及李負責幕前工作，被告聯同黎智英及其助手為幕後負責人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/6CPNWXEDBRFYXHHUX5MALVYWLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2F6CPNWXEDBRFYXHHUX5MALVYWLU%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzviIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=22df8726\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2F6CPNWXEDBRFYXHHUX5MALVYWLU%2F&h=2856bb01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/6CPNWXEDBRFYXHHUX5MALVYWLU/</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"5d3d7be0e31c7d12d622820187894ee80a2e77ff","tid":2488381,"uid":87985,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:14:36.000Z","msg":"佢之前生日，星火有幫佢出post 徵寫信師<br />\n都有相關話題建議<br />\n大家有興趣可以寫信畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjTZoF2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjTZoF2.png&h=c8486a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCredit:星火fb"}}